data.description: 2 MASTER SUITES!  You read that right, located in College Park, this property spans over 2,300 SQFT & features 2 master suites on a split floor plan. Sitting on a corner lot it offers double & single gates, covered patio, & a storage shed that would make a perfect workshop. The interior is spacious boasting an airy open floor plan, sizable living room, family room, dining area, kitchen with breakfast bar, large pantry, gas range & stainless steel appliances. A rare find, this home is a definite must see.
